I wanna talk about the plane crash. Okay?

496
00:33:57.494 --> 00:33:58.577
Sure. what about it?

497
00:33:58.662 --> 00:34:01.497
I was on it. I mean. in it.

498
00:34:01.581 --> 00:34:02.748
I mean. I was in it.

499
00:34:02.833 --> 00:34:04.333
So you were in the plane crash?

500
00:34:04.417 --> 00:34:06.252
I wasn't supposed to be on that plane.
but I was on it.

501
00:34:06.336 --> 00:34:11.340
and there was this guy who was some sort
of secret agent or something. and he...

502
00:34:12.634 --> 00:34:14.385
He killed everybody on board.

503
00:34:15.679 --> 00:34:18.681
And then he landed the plane.
Next thing you know.

504
00:34:18.765 --> 00:34:21.684
I wake up. I'm in my room.
I have no idea how I got there.

505
00:34:21.768 --> 00:34:23.936
He must've drugged me or something.
Then I go to April's fitting.

506
00:34:24.020 --> 00:34:26.105
because I have to wear
this ridiculous dress.

507
00:34:26.189 --> 00:34:28.691
These other guys. these other agents
come. they snatch me up.

508
00:34:28.775 --> 00:34:31.443
Next thing you know.
I'm in Grand Theft Auto on the I-93.

509
00:34:31.528 --> 00:34:34.238
- Why are you touching my hand?
- Because I'm here for you.

510
00:34:34.322 --> 00:34:36.615
- Jeez. you are so stressed out!
- Well. yeah!

511
00:34:36.700 --> 00:34:38.284
- And I get it.
- Really?

512
00:34:38.368 --> 00:34:39.702
I completely understand. I mean...

513
00:34:40.704 --> 00:34:42.079
- Wow. June.
- I know.

514
00:34:42.164 --> 00:34:44.623
- Your little sister's getting married...
- It's like...

515
00:34:44.708 --> 00:34:46.792
