- What are you talking about. Rodney?

516
00:34:46.877 --> 00:34:48.627
You didn't even listen
to what I was talking about.

517
00:34:48.712 --> 00:34:51.797
No. I did. Look. I would probably be
the same way in that situation.

518
00:34:51.882 --> 00:34:54.216
What can I do to help? Setting up?
We can bring the guys over...

519
00:34:54.301 --> 00:34:56.802
No. no. no. Okay.

520
00:34:56.887 --> 00:34:58.137
Oh. Christ.

521
00:34:59.264 --> 00:35:01.307
Hi. June. Look. I...

522
00:35:01.391 --> 00:35:03.392
I'm sorry if I'm interrupting anything. but...

523
00:35:04.519 --> 00:35:05.686
I'm Roy Miller.

524
00:35:06.563 --> 00:35:07.646
Rodney Burris.

525
00:35:07.731 --> 00:35:10.149
Rodney. hi. How are you?

526
00:35:11.318 --> 00:35:14.653
We're running out of time.
and maybe I didn't make it clear enough.

527
00:35:14.738 --> 00:35:19.200
but we're gonna have to stick together
for a little bit. because of our...

528
00:35:19.284 --> 00:35:20.910
You know. our situation.

529
00:35:21.912 --> 00:35:24.330
In case you didn't notice.
Rodney is a fireman. okay?

530
00:35:24.414 --> 00:35:28.000
So he's perfectly capable of handling
any situation that comes up.

531
00:35:28.084 --> 00:35:29.877
Thank you very much.
you can leave us alone.

532
00:35:29.961 --> 00:35:31.170
I have no doubt.

533
00:35:31.254 --> 00:35:35.049
Ever since I was a little kid.
I have great respect for firemen.

534
00:35:35.133 --> 00:35:37.134
- I appreciate it.
- Fact of the matter is.

535
00:35:37.219 --> 00:35:39.011
- I don't think you guys get paid enough.
- Yeah. we don't.

536
00:35:39.095 --> 00:35:40.179
You're in Engine 10.

537
00:35:41.097 --> 00:35:42.264
Yeah. Engine 10.

538
00:35:42.349 --> 00:35:44.433
Yeah. Have you taken
your lieutenant's exam yet?

539
00:35:44.517 --> 00:35:47.353
- I'm working on it.
- Yeah? How's that going?

540
00:35:47.437 --> 00:35:48.729
It's a bitch.

541
00:35:48.813 --> 00:35:50.648
Did you ever do a tour in that hall.
what is it?

542
00:35:50.774 --> 00:35:54.860
Oh. Grove Hall. that's where the action is.
It's the fastest way up the ladder.

543
00:35:54.945 --> 00:35:57.029
- Rodney!
- House of Flames!

544
00:35:58.031 --> 00:35:59.949
I often thought I...

545
00:36:02.327 --> 00:36:04.453
I should have been a fireman.

546
00:36:05.538 --> 00:36:08.207
(SOFTLY) Rodney. this is the guy.

547
00:36:09.417 --> 00:36:10.501
What?

548
00:36:11.670 --> 00:36:14.129
- This is the guy.
- What? "This is the guy"?

549
00:36:15.006 --> 00:36:16.674
I'm sorry. who are you?

550
00:36:18.969 --> 00:36:20.302
I'm the guy?

551
00:36:21.596 --> 00:36:23.097
- I'm the guy. This is the guy.
- This is the guy.

552
00:36:23.181 --> 00:36:24.640
- This is the guy.
- I'm a guy.

553
00:36:24.724 --> 00:36:26.225
- I'm the guy.
- You are a guy.

554
00:36:26.309 --> 00:36:29.270
- I'm a guy.
- JUNE: He's the guy! He's the guy!

555
00:36:29.354 --> 00:36:32.064
- Rodney. whatever happens...
- God.

556
00:36:32.148 --> 00:36:34.149
- Please. for your own safety...
- Rodney. whatever happens.

557
00:36:34.234 --> 00:36:35.693
- you should know...
...please stay in the booth.

558
00:36:36.236 --> 00:36:37.528
What are you talking about?

559
00:36:38.905 --> 00:36:39.905
JUNE: Wait!

560
00:36:39.990 --> 00:36:42.241
Everybody! Everybody get down.

561
00:36:42.325 --> 00:36:44.827
Get down. down. down! Everybody down.

562
00:36:44.911 --> 00:36:47.663
Rodney. get down.
or I will blow her head off.

563
00:36:47.789 --> 00:36:49.164
I'll blow her head off.

564
00:36:50.292 --> 00:36:51.625
- (PATRONS SCREAMING)
- What did I say?

565
00:36:51.710 --> 00:36:53.210
Rodney. what did I say?

566
00:36:53.295 --> 00:36:55.087
- Just calm down. buddy.
- Answer! Huh?

567
00:36:57.632 --> 00:36:59.675
Sorry. I thought you were making a move.

568
00:37:00.051 --> 00:37:02.970
Sorry. It's all right.
I thought he was making a move.

569
00:37:03.054 --> 00:37:05.764
Making a little pie.
Pies for everybody. Everybody.

570
00:37:05.849 --> 00:37:08.100
Everybody gets pies. okay?
No ice-cream. à la mode.

571
