This is gonna be better for you
than Grove Hall. It's all good.

584
00:37:55.732 --> 00:37:58.025
Okay? You good?

585
00:37:58.109 --> 00:37:59.193
- Good?
- Good.

586
00:37:59.277 --> 00:38:00.569
Good?

587
