- What?

603
00:38:59.170 --> 00:39:01.588
Stop the car. Stop the car.
Stop the car. Just stop the car!

604
00:39:01.673 --> 00:39:03.882
June. I understand
you want off the carousel.

605
00:39:03.967 --> 00:39:06.093
