634
00:41:28.861 --> 00:41:32.489
WOMAN ON TV: Rodney. why did you
make this brave call to leap into action?

635
00:41:32.574 --> 00:41:33.615
RODNEY ON TV: Well. I didn't think.

636
00:41:33.700 --> 00:41:35.993
I just did what any man would do
in that situation. you know?

637
00:41:36.077 --> 00:41:37.786
- I leapt into action.
- Thanks.

638
00:41:37.870 --> 00:41:40.914
RODNEY: Like you said. it's really the job.
WOMAN: You should be so proud.

639
00:41:40.999 --> 00:41:42.165
RODNEY: Thanks.
WOMAN: Good job.

640
