643
00:41:50.300 --> 00:41:54.636
A true blue Boston hero. Back to you. Don.

644
00:42:10.194 --> 00:42:11.361
This is what it's all about.

645
00:42:12.071 --> 00:42:14.406
That. right there.
is what everybody wants.

646
