677
00:44:12.108 --> 00:44:15.819
pick up Simon. and get you back
for your sister's wedding.

678
00:44:18.448 --> 00:44:21.700
I'm pretty good at what I do. June.

679
00:44:21.784 --> 00:44:24.953
And tonight. we're safe.

680
00:44:25.788 --> 00:44:27.581
Scout's honor.

681
00:44:29.250 --> 00:44:30.876
Safe and secure?

682
00:44:38.509 --> 00:44:40.510
Good night. Roy.

683
00:44:44.307 --> 00:44:46.475
Were you really a Boy Scout?

684
00:44:48.436 --> 00:44:50.812
Eagle Scout.

685
00:44:52.482 --> 00:44:55.150
I was a Brownie.

686
00:44:55.234 --> 00:44:56.902
- That's cool.
- Mmm.

687
00:45:00.823 --> 00:45:02.824
