688
00:45:20.009 --> 00:45:21.593
MILLER: Pies for everybody. Everybody.

689
00:45:21.677 --> 00:45:24.554
Everybody gets pies. okay?
No ice-cream...

690
00:45:26.015 --> 00:45:29.142
So. what do you think?
Are we looking at another player?

691
