We're looking at a pawn.
I talked to her. so did he.

692
00:45:33.105 --> 00:45:36.399
She owns a garage. no passport.
gone nowhere. been nowhere.

693
00:45:36.526 --> 00:45:38.109
She's a nobody.

694
00:45:38.194 --> 00:45:42.072
