Simon!

700
00:46:12.520 --> 00:46:16.982
I see you. you see me

701
00:46:18.401 --> 00:46:20.110
Simon?

702
00:46:20.736 --> 00:46:24.364
Oh. girl. you've got to know

703
00:46:24.448 --> 00:46:26.032
Stay close.

704
00:46:28.411 --> 00:46:32.247
Hey. Simon. this is no time to play.

705
00:46:32.915 --> 00:46:36.251
You can't escape my

706
00:46:36.335 --> 00:46:40.130
Private eyes
They're watching you

707
00:46:40.214 --> 00:46:43.592
They see your every move

708
00:46:44.260 --> 00:46:45.635
Private eyes

709
00:46:45.720 --> 00:46:48.638
What is all this?

710
00:46:48.723 --> 00:46:51.558
Simon. It's what he does.

711
00:46:53.311 --> 00:46:55.645
I'm late. and he's gone.

712
00:46:57.982 --> 00:47:01.943
You play with words
You play with love

713
00:47:02.570 --> 00:47:06.239
You can twist it around
Baby. that ain't enough

714
00:47:06.324 --> 00:47:10.368
'Cause. girl. I'm gonna know

715
00:47:10.453 --> 00:47:14.164
If you're letting me in or letting me go

716
00:47:14.248 --> 00:47:18.460
Don't lie when you're hurting inside

717
00:47:18.544 --> 00:47:21.129
'Cause you can't escape my

718
00:47:22.006 --> 00:47:24.507
Private eyes
They're watching you

719
00:47:24.592 --> 00:47:26.384
(IMITATING GUNSHOTS)

720
00:47:26.469 --> 00:47:29.846
They see your every move. baby

721
00:47:29.931 --> 00:47:33.683
Private eyes
They're watching you

722
00:47:33.768 --> 00:47:35.310
Mmm-hmm.

723
00:47:36.312 --> 00:47:37.479
Mmm!

724
00:47:45.446 --> 00:47:46.446
