733
00:48:30.866 --> 00:48:32.659
Other bad guys?

734
00:48:32.743 --> 00:48:35.453
Worse guys. Hold my mags.

735
00:48:36.539 --> 00:48:38.248
Worse guys?

736
00:48:38.332 --> 00:48:41.793
Now. I need you to listen carefully.
Do exactly as I say.

737
00:48:41.877 --> 00:48:44.462
