I don't want it someday

1576
01:51:38.692 --> 01:51:42.361
I don't want it one day

1577
01:51:42.446 --> 01:51:45.990
Got to have it somehow

1578
01:51:46.742 --> 01:51:49.619
I want it right now

1579
01:51:51.455 --> 01:51:53.873
I wanna live my life

1580
01:51:53.957 --> 01:51:55.291
MOLLY: Oh. my God. Frank.

1581
01:51:55.375 --> 01:51:57.877
What is this envelope
with tickets to Cape Horn?

1582
01:51:57.961 --> 01:51:59.045
FRANK: What are you talking about?

1583
01:51:59.129 --> 01:52:01.631
MOLLY: Did you order tickets
to South America?

1584
