I don't want it one day

1599
01:52:43.840 --> 01:52:47.927
Gotta have it somehow

1600
01:52:48.011 --> 01:52:51.806
I want it right now

1601
01:52:52.683 --> 01:52:54.558
The past is history. girl

1602
01:52:54.643 --> 01:52:56.602
The future's a mystery. girl

1603
01:52:56.687 --> 01:53:00.439
Today's a precious gift
that's why it's called the present

1604
01:53:00.524 --> 01:53:02.400
I want you night and day. girl

1605
01:53:02.484 --> 01:53:04.151
Come on. let's fly away. girl

1606
01:53:04.236 --> 01:53:08.114
Let's not be scared to have
a little taste of heaven

1607
01:53:08.198 --> 01:53:11.992
'Cause I wanna live my life
no regrets at all

1608
01:53:12.077 --> 01:53:15.413
I'm stumbling onto love
and loving the fall

1609
01:53:15.497 --> 01:53:17.289
I wanna be with you. baby

1610
01:53:17.374 --> 01:53:18.666
And you wanna be with me

1611
