For that someday

1614
01:53:26.049 --> 01:53:29.802
Waiting for the one day

1615
01:53:29.886 --> 01:53:34.014
Gotta have it somehow

1616
01:53:34.099 --> 01:53:37.643
I want it right now

1617
01:53:37.728 --> 01:53:41.439
I don't want it someday

1618
01:53:41.523 --> 01:53:45.234
I don't want it one day

1619
01:53:45.318 --> 01:53:49.321
Gotta have it somehow

1620
01:53:49.406 --> 01:53:52.575
I want it right now

1621
